(3, 3, '', '3_avatar_Zeevyah_Benoff.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1435963, 127, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7dc82c36-205b-cb73-d8f4-b84c97ec2b62\"><span xss=\"removed\">Zeevyah has been a Teaneck resident for over 25 years and has extensive knowledge of the area, local schools and community organizations. Her drive, devotion and creativity have helped her build a successful career in real estate. She prides herself on her negotiation and advocacy skills. </span><span xss=\"removed\"><br class=\"kix-line-break\"></span><span xss=\"removed\">Prior to becoming a real estate professional she worked as a prosecutor in New York City Family Court. Her legal background and keen attention to detail coupled with her candor and energy has positioned her to be an invaluable asset to her clients. She brings a commitment to go above and beyond. </span><span xss=\"removed\"><br class=\"kix-line-break\"></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br class=\"kix-line-break\"></span><span xss=\"removed\">Zeevyah currently lives in the West Englewood section of Teaneck with her husband, Ari Stein and her four young children.</span><span xss=\"removed\"><br class=\"kix-line-break\"></span><span xss=\"removed\"><br class=\"kix-line-break\"></span><span xss=\"removed\">Zeevyah is a member of the National Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors, New Jersey MLS and holds her New York Broker\'s License. She looks forward towards working together with you to find you the perfect home. </span></span>', '', '', 0, 'zeevyah.benoff', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 956-0208', 943945200, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(4, 4, '', '', '', 0, 0, '', '', '', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1531963058, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(5, 5, '', '5_avatar_Alain_Spira.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1540849, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a6790f55-b023-3542-2276-75e84608e5eb\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Alain Spira was born in Antwerp Belgium, and currently resides in Riverdale, NY with his lovely wife and children. He received his MBA from Columbia University and provides clients with a unique perspective, having a background in banking and business. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>A genuine people person with the drive and determination to offer his clients the best service, Alain\'s background and experience have helped him develop a perspective on the market with a special concentration on the financials of a transaction. His focus is working with Real Estate investors and helps keep all eyes on the bottom line.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Alain is a member of the National Association of Realtors, the Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors and the New Jersey MLS.</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(917) 680-1885', 943945200, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(6, 6, '', '6_avatar_Aleshia_Jijon_Headshot_Cropped.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1327287, 202, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-70b28845-b080-92fa-715b-bd2eae64ac4b\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Born and raised in Bergen County, NJ, Aleshia\'s excellent client service stems from her knowledge of the real estate market and corporate marketing background. Her integrity, energy, hard work, and creativity, led her to pursue a successful career in real estate. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Offering a youthful demeanor and experience, she is approachable and adaptive, working well with all her clients to achieve their real estate goals. Specializing in multiple aspects, Aleshia sets a new standard, helping and educating buyers, sellers and investors looking to take the next step! Known by clients and colleagues alike for her tenacity, you can be assured that she will stay on top of all aspects of a deal to provide a smooth and seamless transaction.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Your goals become hers and she will provide a wonderful and successful experience. Aleshia is fluent in Spanish, a member of the National Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors and the New Jersey MLS.</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 647-5153', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(7, 7, '', '7_avatar_AliciaPugh.jpg', 'Broker Associate', 786331, 206, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a45294b3-b09a-23ce-3628-cfbab31f4a99\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Alicia Pugh has been a resident of Bergen County for 28 years. She started her career in Real Estate eight years ago, while still working in corporate America. Her knowledge of the local market makes her a point of contact to put her expertise to work for you, to assist in selling or renting your home and/or finding the home of your dreams. Real estate is a relationship based business and she seeks to create relationships built on trust and honesty. She is committed to giving the attention and support you deserve. Alicia is professional, responsive, helpful, and does everything she can to get results. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Alicia is a firm believer in giving back to the community. Currently she volunteers at a pregnancy resource center, at church, and at the Bogota Library. She is a member of Bogota Beautiful and the Community Service Committee at the Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors. In her spare moments Alicia is reading, quilting, crocheting or just enjoying the outdoors. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Her Motto: Satisfaction 1st; Integrity Always</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Alicia is a member of the National Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors, New Jersey MLS, and Hudson County MLS. She is a designated Seniors Real Estate Specialist®, qualified to address the needs of home buyers and sellers age 50 and over, as well as a designated Short Sales and Foreclosure Resource Specialist® equipped with the skills to help buyers and sellers of distressed properties.</span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, 'Alicia-Pugh-Broker-Associate-141408472605682', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 981-6890', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(8, 8, '', '8_avatar_BrigitteHauyon.jpg', 'Realtor', 12345678, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-15885aa8-b0a3-3089-f834-c863d02f47a0\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Brigitte brings over 13 years of experience in Corporate Finance where she worked with hundreds of clients, business stakeholders, and vendors. Key to her success has always been her strong work ethic, excellent customer service and negotiating skills, her ability to understand peoples’ wants and needs, and her patient, easy-going demeanor. All of these traits will be equally important as she begins her real estate career here at Links. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Brigitte looks forwarding to establishing open communication and working with clients for all of their real estate needs. Her goal is to build lasting relationships while orchestrating deals for both buyers and sellers. You can rest assured that with Brigitte at the helm, she will stay on top of all of the details and provide a smooth transaction.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Brigitte has been a resident of Bergen County for the last 10+ years and has loved every moment of it. She will utilize her inside knowledge and connections within the local markets to find the perfect home for buyers and ensure proper pricing and maximum exposure for sellers. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Brigitte is fluent in both Spanish and Portuguese. She is a member of the National Association of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, and the New Jersey MLS.</span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', 943945200, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(9, 9, '', '9_avatar_BruceEiichman.jpg', 'Broker Manager / Realtor®', 9799220, 129, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-88187a46-b0b1-3afc-af86-2bf6109e382a\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">With over 28 years of experience as a business owner, and as a leading professional in the real estate industry for over 18 years, Bruce brings his seasoned management and marketing skills to the team. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Bruce is a veteran not just in the industry, but for our country as well. He served in the US Army from 1968 -1970 with the Vietnam Combat Duty. He continues to stay involved and gives back to his community, holding numerous positions on various local boards. He served on the Board of Directors for the Jewish Federation, and was the Treasurer of Jewish Family Services of North Jersey. He is a former President of the Veterans Club in Haledon, NJ and was a Chairman of the United Jewish Appeal Campaign in Wayne, NJ.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Bruce is a Licensed Real Estate Instructor for the State of New Jersey, served as the Treasurer for the Bergen County Board of Realtors, and is a member of the Board of Directors for both the Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors Executive Committee and the New Jersey Association of Realtors (NJAR). He is also a part of the NJAR Circle of Excellence Committee.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Along with his endless list of credentials, come Bruce\'s awards. He\'s received the NJAR Million Dollar Circle of Excellence Sales Award on eight different occasions, over the last 15 years.</span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', 'MRP (Military Relocation Professional)', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 294-4858', 943945200, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(10, 10, '', '', 'Broker / Realtor®', 123456789, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ef5a8889-b0b4-db52-e2bf-dc6fd487c08f\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>A 5</span><span xss=removed>th</span><span xss=removed> generation coffee farmer, Carlos has always understood the importance of hard work and persistence. After graduating from Boston University with a degree in Hospitality Administration, he spent a yearlong apprenticeship in San Salvador where he learned all aspects of the coffee production process. From planting the seed to crafting the perfect cup of coffee. His fascination led him to enter into the family coffee business. His passion for satisfying customers, led him into the fast-paced world of restaurant management. Carlos worked in Manhattan at various casual and upscale restaurants as both a Manager and General Manager. In 2008 he began opening start-up restaurants in the Chelsea and Downtown districts of downtown Manhattan. Later in 2013 he opened the Blue Moon Mexican Cafe, a family-operated restaurant and bar in Jersey City, New Jersey. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Carlos comes to Links Residential eager and motivated to begin his real estate career. His passion for customer satisfaction and success in the hospitality industry makes him a natural fit. He is honest, loyal, dependable, and possesses strong leadership and interpersonal skills.  He looks forward to making the client experience as smooth, enjoyable, and memorable as possible.  </span><span xss=removed>“You’re not just investing in a house, you’re creating a home for your family!”</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Carlos is a member of the National Association of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, and New Jersey Multiple Listing Service. A resident of Bergen County for over 15 years, he currently resides in Cliffside Park with his wife and two beautiful daughters. During his free time, Carlos enjoys spending time with his family, kayaking, and looking for ways to stay involved and give back to his community.</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(11, 11, '', '11_avatar_CarolUrena.jpg', 'Sales Associate', 1648649, 220, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7765d009-b0bb-79fc-f45a-4a4756a177b2\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Carol is an outgoing and passionate Realtor with several years of experience. She started her real estate career back in 2012 when she was offered an amazing opportunity to work with a developer in Teaneck where she gained valuable knowledge about being successful and thriving in the real estate industry. With a main focus on acquisitions, she worked as part of a team that closed deals on properties all over New Jersey. Thanks to the support and mentorship from the developer, Carol has been motivated to radiate that same success in the residential market.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Carol provides exceptional support and insight as she works with her clients throughout the entire process of buying or selling a home. Her charismatic energy combined with her strong work ethic ensures great client representation and a smooth transaction. Carol works diligently to understand her clients wants and needs so that she can get the most for them in every transaction.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Carol is a member of the National Association of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, and both the Garden State and New Jersey Multiple Listing Services. She currently resides in East Rutherford where she lives with her family and volunteers for the local little league baseball team, sponsored by Redd’s. In her spare time, Carol enjoys cooking. She looks up new recipes and prepares meals that taste so amazing they would put you in a food coma.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Speak with Carol today to learn how she can best provides service to you for all of your real estate needs!</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 289-2357', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(12, 12, '', '12_avatar_CathyDenissm.jpg', 'Broker Manager / Realtor®', 8439238, 211, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-00fc3fa5-b0c4-add3-74c3-86f24a968d87\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\"><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" xss=\"removed\"> </span></span><span xss=\"removed\">After spending the last 20 years with Century 21 Mainstream, Cathy Denis has finally found her “Home Sweet Home” here at Links Residential. During her tenure at Century 21, Cathy was a top producing realtor her first 10 years and spent the last 10 years as a Broker Owner educating and working with the newer agents that came on board. With over 30 years of real estate knowledge and experience she seeks to continue bringing buyers and sellers together here at Links. Whether you have a large estate, a smaller home, or a rental property you will be treated with the same respect and attention to detail. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Having moved over 25 times before the age of 30, Cathy has experienced the moving process first-hand more times than most would in a lifetime. She currently resides in New Milford where she has been a resident for the last 35 years. Her familiarity with the local market is a major asset and she will do whatever it takes to provide her clients with the best service. When combined, Cathy’s winning attitude, network of professionals, and superb negotiating skills are a recipe for success. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Cathy is a current member of the National Association of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, and New Jersey MLS. She holds the following certifications: Certified Distressed Property Expert, Short Sales, and Senior Moves Specialist.  </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">During her spare time Cathy enjoys spending time with her family, and helping her daughter Kimberly run her own flower company. Cathy believes in life “You are either a Whiner or a Winner, but you can’t be both”. Cathy is most certainly a winner!</span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', 'CDPE (Certified Distressed Property Expert) & SRES (Senior Real Estate Specialist)', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '201.706.7008', '(201) 615-0246', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(13, 13, '', '13_avatar_DaliaSakai.jpg', 'Realtor', 1234567890, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-0b3a5fd5-b0d1-a6f4-e05b-cf8b8861fcc1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A resident of Bergen County for more than 25 years, Dalia brings with her both knowledge and connections in the local markets as she begins her real estate career. Her background as an educator combined with her “people person” mentality has been paramount to her success and satisfaction thus far in her career. As a real estate agent, Dalia enjoys scouting the local area and exploring new neighborhoods. She works tirelessly, investing both time and effort to learn the markets and trends. This positions her to find the perfect HOME for prospective buyers, and get maximum value and exposure for prospective sellers. She prides herself on her ability to understand her clients’ wants and needs. She then works diligently to negotiate with her clients’ best interests in mind. She is eager to share her professional insights to help make YOU a satisfied customer and earn YOUR respect and recommendation.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">This past summer Dalia attended the International Society for Technology in Education (ISTE) conference. There she gained valuable insight into continuously improving her professional practice, modeling lifelong learning, and exhibiting leadership in both her school and community by promoting and demonstrating the effective use of digital tools and resources.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Dalia is a member of the National Association of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, and the New Jersey Multiple Listing Service. During her spare time, Dalia enjoys cooking Persian food, especially for large crowds. She also enjoys swimming and biking, but most importantly – spending time with her beloved family. </span></p><span xss=\"removed\">“</span><span xss=\"removed\">A satisfied customer is the best recommendation”</span></span>', 'test', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '', 943945200, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(14, 14, '', '14_avatar_DaraKlatsky.JPG', 'Realtor', 123, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b836ad01-b0d8-79c7-6835-d6cc57ec3631\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Dara’s strong service oriented background has prepared her well for the diverse personalities and multi-faceted work encountered in real estate industry. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Anyone who has worked with Dara remains consistently impressed with her dedication, creativity and customized service. Her extensive service background and diverse career path spanning athletic training, sales, and administration gave her a solid backbone of skills that serve as her greatest assets today. The impressive track record that she established in these roles was due to her ability to connect with people, earn trust and create lasting relationships.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A graduate of Montclair State University with studies in Athletic Training, she serves as an active member of the Leonia High School Athletic Department, interacting and working with families and students on a daily basis.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Outside of her career in real estate, she loves sports, traveling, and spending quality time with her two cats Lynx and Xena. She supports and donates to ASPCA, helping other animals in need. Dara is consistently exploring new places, taking in all that NJ has to offer, to share those insights with clients, so they too can find the right place to call home.</span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(15, 15, '', '15_avatar_DeborahPearlman.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1751550, 133, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a320fb0e-b0dc-12b8-c214-3f93bb200bea\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Deborah Pearlman recognizes the value of “the look.” With a personal style all her own, she has an innate understanding of what a few small tweaks can do for a new listing or new purchase. “Once the prospective buyers and I have the location and size selected, I enjoy using my design skills to help unlock the potential style and layout that fits each owner’s taste.” Deborah also has a knack for making a listed property more appealing at Open Houses or in property photographs.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Before transitioning to real estate, Deborah spent eight years working in secondary education as a Program Coordinator, highlighting her attentiveness to details big and small. Her work included supervising large-scale programs and events from conception to execution. “Buying a home is one of the most important processes an individual, couple, or family experiences, and someone who can be trusted with overseeing every detail should be at the helm.” She graduated from the Stern College for Women in 2006 with a Bachelors in Science.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Deborah is an active community mom. Her children are heavily involved in regional athletics and competitive dance, which requires professional time-management skills and frequent check-ins, skills she intends to bring to buyers and sellers: “I am always available to manage any number of aspects that can arise from the home-buying process, and I am completely devoted to ensuring my clients\' experiences goes smoothly and in a timely fashion.” She lives in Bergenfield with her husband, caterer David, and three children: Yishaya, Leora, and Sammy. They love to cook dinner as a family and taking trips to unforgettable destinations (dream destinations include Hawaii and Dubai).</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(917) 208-6415', 1531983600, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
