(18, 18, '', '18_avatar_GneshaShain.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1538871, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8ad2ffaf-b0f0-94c6-05d0-0c2a49897ce5\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Born and raised in NY, and  living in the NJ area since 2002, Gnesha brings many years of sales experience and wisdom to all her real estate transactions. Her background in accounting gives her an additional understanding  of her client\'s needs when purchasing and selling properties. Gnesha works with clients patiently, honestly and with integrity, and will be there every step of the way to ensure they achieve their real estate goals. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Gnesha is a member of the National Association of Realtors, the Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors, New Jersey MLS and Ocean County MLS.</span></p></span>', '', '', 0, 'gneshashainrealestate', 'in/gnesha-shain-22b66656', 'gneshashain', 'GneshaShain', '201.706.7008', '(908) 787-6300', 943945200, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(19, 19, '', '19_avatar_JohannaCogan.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1540361, 208, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-eadb2332-b581-258e-53a4-f994fb90c780\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>As a lifelong resident of Bergen County, Johanna has a strong understanding of the New York Metro area.  Whether it is a quiet suburban town or the hustle and bustle of Hoboken, she can find the right place for you.  </span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>After receiving her degree from Rutgers, she worked for  a number of years in Manhattan. Johanna learned at a young age that there is no substitute for integrity and having a strong work ethic. She brings an energetic spirit and commitment, making the purchase or sale of a home a very rewarding and positive experience. Her expertise in the local market and great attention to detail makes her a genuine asset to her clients.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Johanna understands how nerve racking finding a new home can be and will work diligently to make the process as painless and smooth as possible. </span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>In her spare time, Johanna enjoys going to one of the many parks in Bergen County for walks. A mother of two young children, she loves getting together with her family and two dogs. She also works hard alongside her husband to help grow his construction company, Clean Cut Construction in New Milford, NJ. </span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Johanna is a member of the National Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors and the New Jersey MLS.</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '201.706.7008', '(551) 404-3177', 1532070000, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(20, 20, '', '20_avatar_JulieanneDesJardins.jpg', 'Realtor', 12987654, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2167cee0-b583-f11c-4965-2351d897357f\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Julieanne DesJardins joins LINKS RESIDENTIAL in Maywood, New Jersey as a full-time agent and savvy businesswoman.  As a realtor, Julieanne’s hallmark has been extraordinary client service, relationship and business development. Her work ethic, dedication to her clients and commitment to excellence were refined throughout her 30 year career in the prestige cosmetic and skincare industry. Julieanne has brought this expertise to her career in real estate. Her forthright yet sincere and friendly approach always yields a smile from her clients because at the end of the day “realtors need closure”.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Specializing in Bergen County properties, Julieanne brings the breath of her experience to each transaction, giving each valued client a customized advantage throughout the buying and selling process.  Her thorough understanding of real estate trends, market conditions, market value, buyer motivations, selling techniques, strategic marketing and negotiation turn clients into loyal supporters and lifelong friends.  Buyers and sellers can always count on Julieanne to be of service with their home listings or sales.  Buyers can compare locations based on price range, amenities, features and value when seeking their perfect home. Sellers benefit from her detail oriented review of data, pricing and home staging knowledge.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>As a resident of Cliffside Park, N.J, Julieanne enjoys the luxuries of a close knit community and neighborhood establishments.  She spends free time with family and friends enjoying theatre, exercising, spa activities, dining out, traveling and simply enjoying life.  She is active in local and national charities and is a major fundraiser for the Crohn’s and Colitis Foundation, which is dear to her heart.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>As a dynamic businesswoman, Julieanne has continued her education not only in the classroom, but also networking events where she regularly interacts with business leaders and real estate attorneys in addition to title and mortgage company representatives.  She is a member of the Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>If you are looking for someone with expertise and the drive to get the job done, contact Julieanne today.  Her enthusiasm and positive personality will certainly win you over.  Julieanne looks forward to serving you. </span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '201.706.7008', '', 1532070000, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(21, 21, '', '21_avatar_KenGrier.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 9804113, 134, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e3f6f578-b589-e396-4b20-7be0f21ab934\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">\"My objective is to provide customers and clients with the best possible service, utilizing my professional sales experience to their best advantage.\"</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">The opportunity to help others realize their real estate dreams is just one of the reasons Kenneth Grier found his calling as a realtor. His caring, respectful service combined with integrity, professionalism, and an eye for detail make him an ideal choice when you\'re ready to buy or sell a home. </span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Before joining the Links team, Ken was employed as a National Field Sales Manager for the Wella Corporation. He was the founder and President of Grier Sales and Marketing, a sales promotion company. A keen business sense and strong sales background made his move to real estate a natural progression. Ken is a member of the Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, and National Association of Realtors.</span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">A resident of Harrington Park and River Vale for over 40 years, Ken is eager to share his personal knowledge of the Bergen County housing market with customers and clients. </span></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Kenneth has a Bachelor\'s in Marketing from Gannon University and earned his MBA in Marketing from Fairleigh Dickinson. He served his country during the Vietnam era and received an honorable discharge from the United States Army. Ken is a life member and chapter officer in the Disabled American Veterans.Ken is a member of the Knights of Columbus and is a Eucharistic minister at Our Lady of Victories Church in Harrington Park. He enjoys sports, reading, and spending time with his family.</span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 725-4605', 1532070000, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(22, 22, '', '22_avatar_kenSchwartz.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 1540944, 130, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7c43e797-b58f-667a-0a38-58d1a8a74295\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Kenneth is an energetic and hardworking go getter, who loves a challenge and takes great pride in his accomplishments. Your requests and needs will be listened to and become his priority. He strives to make the real estate transaction process smooth and easy, keeping you updated on all aspects of the deal. Along with his extensive knowledge in the real estate industry, you can rely on his attention to detail, reliability, loyalty, and honesty. With experience in construction and remodeling, he has a keen eye for finding the hidden potentials within a home. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>If you want it, he\'ll find it. If you have it, he\'ll sell it. Kenneth works tirelessly to help you reach your real estate goals.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Kenneth is a member of the National Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors, and New Jersey MLS. </span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, 'Ken-Schwartz-Realtor-Associate-LINKS-Residential-1584032078579075/', 'in/kenneth-schwartz-b4ab50108/', 'schwartz.kenneth/', 'KenJaySchwartz', '(201) 706-7008', '(201) 365-8086', 1532070000, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(23, 23, '', '23_avatar_LioraKirsch.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 654321234, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2daf9f1e-b593-aa2a-fd38-23b2959d691e\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Liora Kirsch was born in Israel, and split her time growing up between Tel Aviv and the New York metro area. Her multicultural background offers her clients an understanding and insight only a select few are able to provide. Liora has 25 years of experience in sales and marketing and for the last 10 years, has been deep-rooted in the local real estate market servicing hundreds of homebuyers and sellers alike throughout Bergen and Hudson County. Her strengths are in customer service and really listening to her client\'s needs. She is willing to give 110% to her clients and has a strong following coupled with high marks in service and loyalty.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Liora currently resides in Teaneck with her 3 lovely children. She is a member of the National Association of Realtors, Eastern Bergen Board of Realtors, and the New Jersey MLS.</span></p><div><span xss=removed><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '(201) 706-7008', '', 1532070000, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),
(24, 24, '', '24_avatar_LuisGutierrez.jpg', 'Sales Associate / Realtor®', 65434565, 0, '<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e343ae8e-b59d-6305-fd3d-a1056fba8999\"><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Unmistakable energy. Incredible negotiation skills. Persistence and dedication.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Luis Gutierrez possesses an innate understanding and keen awareness of what it takes to be a top Realtor®. “I believe the customers’ needs and concerns are my number one priority. My goal is to be available to work with their best interests in mind – all the time.”</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Luis was born in Cuba, and moved to the United States at 8 years old.  He grew up in Hudson County, and studied Business at Middlesex County College. Luis is the founder of Imperial Group, a team of real estate agents specializing in Bergen, Hudson & Passaic Counties.  He uses his 14 years business experience to lead them, and his knowledge and foresight successfully achieves his client’s goals. He and his team communicate with buyers, sellers and renters in every detail of a transaction, from the first phone call all the way to close.  “I pride myself on exceptional service and negotiation skills, and I enjoy helping people achieve the American Dream just as I did.”</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Luis resides in _________________ with his wife and two beautiful children. He is a member of the National Association of Realtors, the Young Professionals Network (YPN), Eastern Bergen County Board of Realtors, New Jersey Association of Realtors, New Jersey MLS, Garden State MLS, Central Jersey MLS, and Hudson County MLS.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" xss=\"removed\"><span xss=\"removed\">Five words you can count on when working with Luis Gutierrez? Integrity, commitment, passion, personable, productive. </span></p><div><span xss=\"removed\"><br></span></div></span>', '', '', 